766
00:56:48,380 --> 00:56:50,850
Oh, okay.

767
00:57:12,640 --> 00:57:15,480
Your love line is very good.

768
00:57:15,480 --> 00:57:17,530
You will meet someone nice soon.

769
00:57:20,630 --> 00:57:23,090
Brother.

770
00:57:23,090 --> 00:57:25,840
I wish you all the best.

771
00:57:30,830 --> 00:57:32,760
I wish you all the best too.

772
00:57:36,350 --> 00:57:40,010
Now we are rivals.

773
00:57:40,010 --> 00:57:42,340
I'm just going to produce Hitman.

774
00:57:42,340 --> 00:57:45,240
I'm not good at business.

775
00:57:45,240 --> 00:57:48,770
