781
00:58:22,590 --> 00:58:24,310
Which ones?

782
00:58:24,310 --> 00:58:27,590
About Ryu Hae Sung's secret story.

783
00:58:27,590 --> 00:58:30,140
Whatever the reason is,
if it gets leaked to the media

