information in your budget.

792
00:58:54,010 --> 00:58:55,870
That way, we can plan our budget too.

793
00:58:55,870 --> 00:58:59,250
This is the contract that I made.
Please take a look at this.

794
00:59:05,270 --> 00:59:06,800
Then I can't sign this contract.

795
00:59:06,800 --> 00:59:13,450
