801
00:59:37,810 --> 00:59:39,730
Okay. Let's surprise him.

802
00:59:39,730 --> 00:59:42,020
I will do your makeup that day.

803
00:59:42,020 --> 00:59:43,620
I will cook.

804
00:59:46,160 --> 00:59:47,910
Our So Hye looks so pretty.

