825
01:00:58,220 --> 01:01:01,190
Really?

826
01:01:01,550 --> 01:01:03,310
Let's not do that.

827
01:01:06,130 --> 01:01:09,540
It's great to live in a
house together, right?

828
01:01:09,540 --> 01:01:12,300
Once my mom gets better

829
