I will stay by your side
all day, every day.

830
01:01:15,560 --> 01:01:19,940
Let's grow old together.

831
01:01:19,940 --> 01:01:26,480
Okay. Until we become grandmothers,
let's stick tightly together.

832
01:01:41,430 --> 01:01:44,020
